{
  "stem": "26111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I will never forget the-- I think the first time that my father really had it brought home to him-- and I mean home-- what the situation was was at the end of a-- for Whitsuntide, for, for Pfingsten, as it's called.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This, this, this was a popular holiday, same as Easter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And people had, had-- it was a national holiday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Pfingsten, usually what you did, you went out into the countryside, and you came back with green branches.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a kind of a spring holiday, beginning of summer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was in May.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you came back, and you decorated your house or your apartment with these branches.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, we had been out in the car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had this open car that was seen on the-- on-- the convertible that you'd seen on the photo.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we drew up in front of our house-- let us out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my father would drive into the garage after we'd got out, my, my mother and sister and I.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got out, and I wasn't looking at the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was looking at something else on this side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw my father-- my father's face turned to stone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- he was looking at the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I looked at the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, as I mentioned before, his practice was in the-- in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there was his professional sign-- it was copper, or whatever they, they, they have-- as a doctor was, was right fixed and in front of the door-- by, by the side of the door.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
